abstract: David Hearn shoots seven-under-par 64 to share lead in Shriners Hospitals for Children Open with Michael Thompson, Mark Hubbard and Tyler Aldridge.
lead_paragraph: Hearn birdied his final three holes for a seven-under-par 64 and a share of the lead in the Shriners Hospitals for Children Open in Las Vegas.

headline.main: David Hearn Has Share of Lead
